This is was a birthday gift to myself when i turned 30. This was so far my only out of country workshop to my favorite mentor @moka_photographie , to a country i dont even speak the language (french). Lol. But it was such an amazing trip. Beautiful Caribbean  island. So many great spots to shoot photos. And we had the best time just hanging out. Not only does @moka_photographie have amazing knowledge about photoshoot also she is amazing mentor to give and help others. Her editing is beyond the words. We had studio shoot, jungle river shoot and beach photoshoot together. This trip will always be a highlight in my life. Thank you @moka_photographie.

So you probably realize by now that i love being part of and helping the photo community. So i hosted another workshop at my studio. 😊 now usually i host maternity specific workshops but this time it was more of a fine art portrait type workshop. Always be learning new things! We had such a great group in the studio, everyone so nice. And such a pleasure to have teacher @johngressmedia to show us all some new things. And as a bonus we had @loveprintphotography helping out, always nice having Diana in the studio again, shes such a special  friend and mentor. So photography, dinner and new friends. Such a special few days. Learning.Everyday. Thanks everyone!

Now i think its clear that this was an amazing workshop. I mean wow. Underwater photography workshop in the crystal clear waters of the Florida springs. Be thanks to @waterbearphotography for showing us something unique and special. The photos we got were so in tune with nature and organic but not something you usually see. And the people were so fun and nice. We had such a great group. Cant wait for a chance to go back.

Celebrate This Father’s Day with a One-of-a-Kind Daddy and Me Photo Shoot! 

Dads play so many roles in our lives. They’re the superheroes who protect us, the trees that keep the rain off our heads, and the friends who always know how to make us smile. The bond between a father and his child is unlike any other, and it deserves to be celebrated and preserved forever.

In honor of Father’s Day, give the special dad in your life the gift of lifelong memories with a Daddy and Me photo shoot. This unique photography session is all about giving dads a chance to spend quality time doing something fun with their kids while also creating beautiful portraits the entire family will treasure. We don’t have our dads forever, so now is the time to enjoy these special experiences with him. For your own dad, your husband, your child’s father, or other beloved father figures in your life, this is a Father’s Day gift that keeps giving.

Book your Daddy and Me session at Fangting Photography today!

Hi Everyone. Let me introduce myself again. My name is Fangting and for more than 12 years, I have been putting my passion to work as a professional photographer and I have the privilege of saying that I love what I do!
 
Photography is an art form that allows me to capture the beauty of truth in the most monumental times of my clients’ lives, and I would be honored to share this experience with you.

Make up/ Hair @uniqueandflawless

Newborn photography is a gift to yourself that you’ll be grateful for in the years to come, and at Fangting Photography, we would be honored to make it happen.
 
You’re preparing for one of the most exceptional and life-changing experiences: welcoming your new baby. It’s truly miraculous to watch how quickly your baby grows and changes, and in a matter of weeks, you’ll be thrilled to see your baby growing yet sad to leave behind the days when they were teeny and curled up. Newborn photography gives you top-quality portraits of your baby’s first days so you can preserve these memories for a lifetime. Fangting Photography creates truly one-of-a-kind newborn photos and custom portraits you’ll treasure.

It’s never too early to start dreaming about the gorgeous newborn photos you can bring home for your new bundle of joy. Explore our newborn photography video to see what we’ve created for other new families and get inspiration for the styles and portraits you want.

Can’t wait to see you and your family.

Floor backdrop @hsdbackdrops 
Video @joemcphotovideo 
Make up/ hair: @uniqueandflawless

Baby photography is a gift to yourself that you’ll be grateful for in the years to come, and at Fangting Photography, we would be honored to make it happen.

A sitter session is a photo session taken when your baby is newly sitting up on their own – usually around 6-9 months. It’s a perfect way to get those first hints of your baby’s one-of-a-kind personality into long-lasting photos before they start walking.
 
Every sleepless night you spend comforting your crying baby may feel long, but in the blink of an eye your baby won’t be such a baby anymore, and you’ll be searching for the memories of those tiny fingers and tiny toes. That’s why we’re here. At Fangting Photography, our boutique custom photography studio in San Diego, we preserve the memories of these precious days so you can revisit them in a heartbeat, all while creating gorgeous fine art you can enjoy on your walls and bookshelves for decades to come.
